Common.SpaceDescription.Common.Text:
This recently updated space is available for immediate occupancy. Located
at the intersection of Fountain Blvd and Powers Blvd, 1925
Aerotech Drive is positioned in Colorado Springs’ Defense Contractor
Corridor and offers easy access to many hotel, restaurant and retail
amenities. Features include exterior/private entrance, building and
monument signage (visible from Fountain Blvd), large kitchen/breakroom,
in-suite restrooms, and mountain views from the quiet courtyard.
Floorplan offers private offices of many sizes, partially furnished
training, conference and meeting rooms, and large auditorium with
capacity for up to 80 people.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: NEC Chapel Hills Drive and Briargate Parkway

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Pine Creek Village Center

Located just minutes from The Promenade Shops at Briargate and the Chapel Hills Mall which consists of national and regional retail tenants and restaurants. Perfect for retail shop, coffee shop, breakfast or lunch spot, medical or therapy office! Enjoy majestic mountain views, easy access to I-25, and town center ambience with many walkable amenities in one of Colorado Springs’ most prestigious communities.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: The property is located in the I-25 corridor at the North Gate Blvd exit, with uninterrupted west facing views of the Front Range.
Situated across from the Air Force Academy, this high-income area is experiencing a substantial amount of new residential and commercial growth.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This newly constructed building is the corporate headquarters for Covington Homes. The available office space includes access and usage of common area restrooms, potential for an en suite kitchenette, and existing exclusive use of outside shaded patio. Buildout options include hard walled offices and conference rooms.

Excellent office space is now available in this well-maintained office building in southwest Colorado Springs. Desirable property at 620 Southpointe is just minutes from downtown and offers great visibility and easy access from Lake Avenue. Great opportunity to secure move-in ready small office space at below market rates. Many long term tenants in this building.
